\par\plain {\f0\fs28\b0 Relief washed over him as a notification finally appeared on his screen. It was her response. His heart, which had been clenched tight with worry, began to uncoil as he read her words. She had seen his message while she was shopping, and she'd simply forgotten to reply.}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\cf5 <$Scr_Cs::1> <!$Scr_Cs::1>}{\f1\fs28\i1\cf4 <$Scr_Cs::0>An oversight. Just an oversight,<!$Scr_Cs::0>}{\f0\fs28\b0  he repeated to himself, a mixture of joy and lingering confusion swirling within him. How had something so simple, so mundane, turned into a source of such distress? He realized that the void left by their fading friendship had been filled with insecurities and doubts, magnifying every small misstep into a possible catastrophe. A smile tugged at his lips as he started to type back, gratitude and warmth flowing through his fingers. They were still connected, still friends, and a forgotten message wouldn't change that.}{ }}